| If you change... | It breaks... | You must also update... |
|-----------------|-------------|------------------------|
{% if impact_matrix %}
{% for item in impact_matrix %}
| `{{ item.component }}` | {{ item.breaks }} | {{ item.also_update }} |
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
| `app/models/<entity>.py` (add/remove field) | Pydantic schemas, Alembic migrations, API response | `app/schemas/<entity>_schema.py`, `alembic/versions/`, `openapi.yaml` |
| `app/schemas/<entity>_schema.py` (change field type) | Route handlers, tests, API consumers | `app/routes/<entity>_routes.py`, `tests/test_contracts.py`, `openapi.yaml` |
| `openapi.yaml` (change endpoint path/method) | Route file, test file, any client consuming it | `app/routes/`, `tests/test_contracts.py` |
| `app/auth_config.py` (change JWT claims) | All routes using `get_current_user`, tenant middleware | `app/middleware/tenant_middleware.py`, all route handlers |
| `app/middleware/tenant_middleware.py` | All data queries — potential data leak | `tests/test_tenant_isolation.py` MUST still pass |
| `app/database.py` (change session factory) | Every route using `Depends(get_db)` | All route files, all test fixtures in `tests/conftest.py` |
| `app/main.py` (add/remove middleware) | Security posture, rate limits, CORS | `tests/test_security_owasp.py`, `tests/test_contracts.py` |
{% endif %}

